spec_data.Name: python2-walkdir
spec_data.Description:
walkdir is a simple set of iterator tools intended to
make it easy to manipulate and filter the output of os.walk()
in a way that is also easily applicable to any source iterator
that produces data in the same format
spec_data.Signature: RSA/SHA256, Sat 29 Jul 2017 05:03:06 AM EDT, Key ID f55e7430f5282ee4
spec_data.Summary: Python module to manipulate and filter os.walk() style iteration
